<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink332">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi yeṉṉatūu</l>
<l>maṟaṉila maṉṟa tāmē viṟaṉmicaik</l>
<l>kuṉṟukeḻu kāṉatta paṇpiṉ mākkaṇaṅ</l>
<l>koṭitē kātalip pirital</l>
<l>cella laiya veṉṉā tavvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>Those worthless herds of animals </l>
<l>in the groves on great elevated mountains </l>
<l>don’t have even a little bit of virtue! </l>
<l>None of them says: “Separation from the beloved is harsh! </l>
<l>Don’t leave, o lord!”  </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
